Package: wickracompile
Type: Package
Title: Compile a Wickra Strategy Spec to a Standalone Deployable
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("kingchenc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@wickra.org")
Description: R bindings for wickra-compile over its C ABI hub: a strategy spec
    is compiled into a standalone deployable and a byte-identical manifest -
    the same protocol as the CLI and every other binding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE | Apache License 2.0
URL: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-compile
BugReports: https://github.com/wickra-lib/wickra-compile/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
NeedsCompilation: yes
SystemRequirements: the wickra-compile C ABI shared library (WKCOMPILE_LIB)
    and its header (WKCOMPILE_INC).
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
